title: #92Noon! Micheletti/Chavous/Dilfer/Gleeman!
description: We start by Wolves, followed by Pat Micheletti's thoughts on the Wild and Chuck Fletcher's dismissal. Corey Chavous on the NFL draft, NFL Net's Trent Dilfer, with Aaron Gleeman in studio for most of the final hour!
